snippet: A chase that began Monday with two men in an S.U.V. firing on pursuing police officers ended several hours later with one suspect dead, another arrested and a SWAT officer with a gunshot wound to the leg.
abstract: Police chase in Los Angeles, Calif, of two men driving recklessly in an SUV firing on pursuing police officers ends with one suspect dead, another arrested and a SWAT officer wounded.
lead_paragraph: A chase that began Monday with two men in an S.U.V. firing on pursuing police officers ended several hours later with one suspect dead, another arrested and a SWAT officer with a gunshot wound to the leg.

headline.main: California: Shootout and Chase End in One Death and Arrest
